{"tid":1127814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[巔峰對決] 兩個女人撞衫 邊個正D??","createTime":"2019-04-27T11:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T08:05:11.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1015,"dislike":263,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8af59134557caf6430d5245dcdc048f45ad331b3","tid":1127814,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:14:31.000Z","msg":"女團 BlackPink 成員 Jisoo 和 Twice 成員多賢穿了一樣的衣服<br />\n<br />\n2 月 11 日，BlackPink 成員金智秀在美國 CBS 深夜脫口秀節目 The Late Show with Stephen Colbert 上穿了一件黑色單露肩上衣和黑色短褲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://images6.fanpop.com/image/photos/42600000/BLACKPINK-at-The-Late-Show-with-Stephen-Colbert-black-pink-42634829-730-730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages6.fanpop.com%2Fimage%2Fphotos%2F42600000%2FBLACKPINK-at-The-Late-Show-with-Stephen-Colbert-black-pink-42634829-730-730.jpg&h=4cc99985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vinashowbiz.com/News/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/blackpink-bi-che-mot-dieu-nay-khi-trinh-dien-tren-song-truyen-hinh-my-c86fa5c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvinashowbiz.com%2FNews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Fblackpink-bi-che-mot-dieu-nay-khi-trinh-dien-tren-song-truyen-hinh-my-c86fa5c4.jpg&h=8406988a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images6.fanpop.com/image/photos/42600000/BLACKPINK-at-The-Late-Show-with-Stephen-Colbert-black-pink-42634846-730-730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages6.fanpop.com%2Fimage%2Fphotos%2F42600000%2FBLACKPINK-at-The-Late-Show-with-Stephen-Colbert-black-pink-42634846-730-730.jpg&h=651749b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在4 月22 日，Twice 成員多賢在迷你專輯《FANCY YOU》的發售紀念Showcase 活動上也穿了和智秀一樣的衣服，在這次Twice 的回歸中，多賢染了個二次元髮色，配上白皙的額皮膚，散發出引人注目的成熟魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/26Y4hfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F26Y4hfb.jpg&h=31c51e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D4vbs4NUIAEsi7H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD4vbs4NUIAEsi7H.jpg&h=cb213f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJISOO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613a10eacfc3a3187acec94631994a6af8431f71","tid":1127814,"uid":74065,"like":77,"dislike":12,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"一些網友和粉絲的評論：<br />\n- 說實話，這衣服Jisoo 穿起來更好看；<br />\n- Jisoo 的美貌指數果然不一樣，實在太漂亮了；<br />\n- 智秀穿起來漂亮多了； - 多賢很可愛啊，皮膚真白；<br />\n- 肯定是智秀更漂亮啊，這還用說；<br />\n- 我覺得模特穿的最好看，也最合適；<br />\n- Jisoo 穿出了高級感，而多賢~一般；<br />\n- 多賢很可愛，不過不是很適合這件衣服；<br />\n- 只有我覺得這件衣服很難看嗎？誰穿都算不上好看；<br />\n- 完全沒有可比性，身材、顏值都是 Jisoo 完勝好嗎；"},{"pid":"6ae797e761cd585bc4248896a9f9935716a1581e","tid":1127814,"uid":223790,"like":146,"dislike":8,"score":138,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ec42e71ff79a948d994fc0862cc34756ae33972","tid":1127814,"uid":88491,"like":89,"dislike":5,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"完全沒有可比性，身材、顏值都是 Jisoo 完勝好嗎"},{"pid":"bb25a6ba93a6f41d99762148395053ac8230d3f5","tid":1127814,"uid":88491,"like":14,"dislike":17,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6ae797e761cd585bc4248896a9f9935716a1581e","tid":1127814,"uid":223790,"like":146,"dislike":8,"score":138,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"做乜9 =.="},{"pid":"ae60273f82924ae9ba2b2fef1f8bde971bc97543","tid":1127814,"uid":193693,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"件衫好核突，<br />\n仲要公主膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"fe402c53443b9caaf89f3e6fdd65240203f282fd","tid":1127814,"uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:19:50.000Z","msg